text: <@U0P2GSA8Z> I missed the TSC session and had a question that wasn't answered by reading the minutes. Are more explicit distinctions being considered along lines of, for example, architecture vs. requirements vs. suitability for a purpose vs. software dev process maturity?

<@U14KZA474>: overall there seems to be agreement that we can't define a set list of specific criteria that will work for all cases and whatever we put forward is merely to be used as guidance. With that in mind I think we could certainly expand on the type of criteria put forward. If you could propose specific items to be added to the list that'd be great.
